<v Speaker 2>Comes lo que prefieras.

00:03:30.220 --> 00:03:35.099
<v Speaker 1>Comes lo que prefieras would be you eat whatever you prefer.

00:03:34.940 --> 00:03:37.260
<v Speaker 1>Comes lo que prefieras.

