00:04:12.700 --> 00:04:15.340
<v Speaker 2>Come lo que prefieras.

00:04:15.340 --> 00:04:15.819
<v Speaker 1>Very good.

00:04:15.819 --> 00:04:17.820
<v Speaker 1>Come lo que prefieras.

00:04:17.820 --> 00:04:19.579
<v Speaker 1>Now make this formal.

00:04:19.579 --> 00:04:23.180
