<v Speaker 2>Coman lo que prefieran.

00:04:47.520 --> 00:04:47.920
<v Speaker 1>Good.

00:04:47.920 --> 00:04:49.840
<v Speaker 1>Coman lo que prefieran.

00:04:49.840 --> 00:04:50.480
